# Podracer Credentials
# Copy this file's instructions to set up your credentials.
# Each credential is a separate file in this directory.
# These files are gitignored.

# --- hf_token ---
# HuggingFace token for speaker diarization (pyannote models)
# Get one at: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# Save to: .credentials/hf_token
# Contents: just the token string, e.g. hf_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# --- openrouter_token ---
# OpenRouter API key for cloud summarization
# Get one at: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Save to: .credentials/openrouter_token
# Contents: just the key string, e.g. sk-or-xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# --- podcast_index ---
# Podcast Index API credentials for podcast search
# Sign up at: https://api.podcastindex.org/signup
# Save to: .credentials/podcast_index
# Contents (two lines):
# PODCAST_INDEX_API_KEY=your_key_here
# PODCAST_INDEX_API_SECRET=your_secret_here
